flowRoot.flowPara: The default state of the toolbar is a page title (along with domain subtitle). Clicking the title will transform it into an entry widget.
The reload button is available when the typed URL of the page matches the one of the loaded document.
Blank page doesn't show the title, but the URL entry even if unfocused.
Search the web or type in URL
Unfocusing the URL bar if the typed text differes from the loaded page URL will keep the URL entry rather than changing to a page title.
